{"tid":840925,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【#Cult片】又係Torma 《Father's Day 父親劫 》","createTime":"2018-09-29T07:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T20:39:02.000Z","uid":212112,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56b9a4f27514c211374df56017a27447d98f9a82","tid":840925,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/152635_1839199720f3423b9f2fc81f1d326718.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F152635_1839199720f3423b9f2fc81f1d326718.png&h=3b9d424a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正所謂Torma出品必屬Cult品<br />\n<br />\n劇情講述獨眼復仇者在童年目睹父親節當日變態殺人魔雞姦虐殺自己父親，多年以來無法釋懷的他想為父報仇卻被殺人魔玩弄於鼓掌。後來加入了神父和父親同樣被雞姦慘死於殺人魔手中的叛逆少年的組合之後，局面似乎有了轉機。然而過世的神父留下的一本筆錄卻讓眾人陷入恐慌，變態殺人魔似乎不僅僅是個熱衷於父親節那天獵殺父親們的一般魔頭⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/152637_a466fc1a92a5df9e619fc9035a16f331.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F152637_a466fc1a92a5df9e619fc9035a16f331.png&h=04dabf3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Father's Day》不管是製作上或是畫面處理上，過分玩弄骯髒低級和血腥的元素，離經叛道的放肆惡搞，甚至大畫面描述陽具特寫和各種裸露色情表現，讓你目不轉睛和直冒冷汗。<br />\n電影基本上可以分為兩個階段性的轉變，前半段單純屬於暴力犯罪電影模式，主要描述現實生活中的烏煙瘴氣，叛逆少年和朋友的為非作歹，和父親間的矛盾爭執，強調著破碎家庭問。<br />\n而電影的後半段劇情可謂一隻脫韁野馬，大量動畫特效與早期恐怖電影化妝技巧，還有血漿大平賣與內臟亂飛，充滿歌德風格的佈景與本片前半大相徑庭，惡搞的血腥，最後主角還吞槍自殺穿越時空又上天堂又下地獄，最終boss居然是地獄妖魔讓人感到本片就是一場笑話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/152639_eac53aa5e5d1c0e60d4e99509104152e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F152639_eac53aa5e5d1c0e60d4e99509104152e.png&h=6b71a84c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，影片亦忽然間穿插一個白癡到極點的&rdquo;偽電影預告片&rdquo;，就像Quentin Tarantino和Robert Rodriguez的《Death Proof》《Planet Terror》，導演很用心拍攝一小段只有簡單雛形，剪成一兩分鐘看似精采的預告片段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/152641_7a22948cc10631b24afd4d64a939b993.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F152641_7a22948cc10631b24afd4d64a939b993.png&h=333ea567&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/152643_b4eeceec6ab8f83e604c484db5783c93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F152643_b4eeceec6ab8f83e604c484db5783c93.png&h=2f00f14c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/152645_fc5de938b134b9c1da9d640f5bb07217.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F152645_fc5de938b134b9c1da9d640f5bb07217.png&h=2aa75f98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/152646_6c8b2e3c45e6b57d306d141335edbf71.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F152646_6c8b2e3c45e6b57d306d141335edbf71.png&h=627b47ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/152649_7f99a0200080c436fa3a368aa9b5a896.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F152649_7f99a0200080c436fa3a368aa9b5a896.png&h=8587b4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BoPgCT4haSa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBoPgCT4haSa%2F&d=q6AjDh8bRvErRVkXioxesTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=fca320d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBoPgCT4haSa%2F&h=2b19eb21\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/p/BoPgCT4haSa/</a>"},{"pid":"d943f0cee4cba95b0b7311cea30ed0d1eeefea34","tid":840925,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg